{"parse":{"title":"Icefin Bluefish","pageid":86152,"wikitext":{"*":"<onlyinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|icon=INV_Misc_Fish_23\n|stack=20\n|name=Icefin Bluefish\n|quality=Common\n|sell={{cost|||8}}\n|ilvl=60\n}}</onlyinclude>\n\n== Source ==\nYou can fish for this at many locations in [[Nagrand]],\nas well as in the [[Eco-Dome Midrealm]] in [[Netherstorm]].\n\nExact values are hard to guess, but it may take an effective fishing\nskill of 425 or greater to reel these in.  That is, your fishing skill,\nplus the effects of your [[Fishing Pole]], [[Lure]], and any gear you\ncarry that adds to your fishing skill.\n\nShares pool spawn locations with [[Pure Water]] and [[Figluster's Mudfish]].\n\n== Icefin Bluefish as an Ingredient ==\n\n'''Icefin Bluefish''' is used to make {{loot|common|Poached Bluefish}}.\n\n==See also==\n*[[Fishing]]\n\n== Patch changes ==\n{{Patch 2.0.1|note=Added in [[Burning Crusade]].}}\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|27437}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/icefin_bluefish.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common fished items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft cooking ingredient items]]\n[[Category:Fish]]"}}}